Package edu.uky.cs.nil.sabre.bench

Class Report

java.lang.Object
edu.uky.cs.nil.sabre.bench.Report
public class Report extends Object
A report is a collection of information, mostly organized into tables, about the results of testing many planners on many benchmark problems.
Author:
Stephen G. Ware

    • addProblem

      public void addProblem(Benchmark benchmark, edu.uky.cs.nil.sabre.util.Worker.Status status)
      Adds details for a new benchmark problem to the problems table. This method will ground and then simplify a problem so that statistics about the ground problem can be added to the table.
      Parameters:
      benchmark - the new benchmark problem to add
      status - a status to update while the problem is compiled
